<div class="intro">
    <p>Review</p>    <p>&#34;&#39;You will have three reasons to love this book. It&#39;s about national income differences within the modern world, perhaps the biggest problem facing the world today. It&#39;s peppered with fascinating stories that will make you a spellbinder at cocktail parties - such as why Botswana is prospering and Sierra Leone isn&#39;t. And it&#39;s a great read. Like me, you may succumb to read...</p><p><a href="javascript:void(0)" class="j a_show_full">(展开全部)</a></p></div>
