                <blockquote><q>In most Latin American countries, however, the political institutions there created a very different outcome. Frontier lands were allocated to the politically powerful and those with wealth and contacts, making such people even more powerful.</q></blockquote>
剥夺人民财产权，大批的土地、企业、金融涌向权贵，于是便财富和权力开始集中。
